modName: The Stockade - A World of Warcraft dungeon in Skyrim
summary: Well, I used to play WoW in the past, and when I saw Solitude\'s Dungeon I tell myself that I could make something to improve the city, so I did.
descriptionHtml:
-IF SOMEONE WANT TO HELP ME TO MAKE THIS MOD BETTER TELL ME BY MESSAGE-

Si buscas la traducción española mira este archivo: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16442


I present The Stockade, a remake of the original WoW Dungeon, featuring Defias bandits (Now with a black hood) and the same bosses, including Hamhock the ogre and the dwarfs.
The entrance is under the Solitude Arch, where you can descend to the port.

This dungeon is just for fun for High Levels, but it could be challenging to new players, you can bring your companion to help you to get the aggro (I had to work on it, at the beggining there was mass battles haha) 


Known Bugs:
None now (I hope)
If you see some kind of bug report it to me by message.


I know that the dungeon is not an exact copy, but I\'m very busy and I need first some community support to continue on it, so if I get about 20 endorsements (or many downloads) I will update it with quest, better cells (not the similar matrix for all), and more!
author: Kenta150
